05:57.267 --> 06:04.978
And God will put your life back together when you get into church and you get submitted and committed, amen?

06:05.154 --> 06:07.999
So wisdom is coming to church, amen?

06:08.480 --> 06:11.105
I'm looking at people of wisdom out here, amen?

06:11.466 --> 06:12.207
Glory to God.

06:12.748 --> 06:15.693
And watching me online, that's a lot of wisdom, amen?

06:16.294 --> 06:19.320
And wisdom is greater than foolishness in Proverbs 8, 12.

06:19.340 --> 06:26.674
It says, I wisdom dwell with prudence, and I find out knowledge and discretion.

06:26.894 --> 06:27.375
Praise God.

06:28.096 --> 06:29.138
Then we found out,

06:29.218 --> 06:31.942
Last week, that praise is greater than complaining.

06:32.422 --> 06:36.368
How many people stopped complaining after my message on Sunday, amen?

06:36.828 --> 06:45.580
When we found out complaining is right in line with idolatry and sexual sins, we don't wanna be complaining, amen?

06:46.101 --> 06:49.105
And praise God, what should we be doing?

06:49.125 --> 06:53.571
Well, in Hebrews 13, 15, it says, therefore, by Him, let us continually.

06:53.932 --> 06:55.634
Somebody say continually.

06:56.290 --> 07:03.558
All for the sacrifice to praise the God, that is the fruit of our lips, given thanks to His name.

07:03.998 --> 07:10.945
So it's not just being thankful in yourself, it's giving God praise out of your lips.

07:11.446 --> 07:14.209
How many praiseers do I have in the house today?

07:14.249 --> 07:16.531
I'm looking at some praiseers, amen.

07:16.992 --> 07:23.218
And of course, you know, the old cliche, you complain, you remain, and you praise, and you be raised, amen.

07:23.394 --> 07:28.120
And so let's look at our main text that we've been looking at for the entire series.

07:28.200 --> 07:30.122
And it's based on Matthew 633.

07:31.364 --> 07:45.882
And Jesus is talking about in this chapter that the world is seeking things, seeking financial blessings and all that and trying to seek the things.

07:45.982 --> 07:48.565
