07:49.646 --> 07:50.547
I'm going to say that again.

07:50.707 --> 07:52.850
If you put God first place,

07:53.666 --> 07:55.188
things will come into your life.

07:55.248 --> 07:57.330
Blessings will come into your life.

07:57.991 --> 08:11.466
And it says here in the Amplified, but first and most importantly, seek aim at and strive after his kingdom and his righteousness, his way of doing and being right.

08:12.327 --> 08:15.370
Somebody say God's way and not my way.

08:16.732 --> 08:22.418
And the attitude and character of God, all these things will be given to you also.

08:22.882 --> 08:23.683
So I love that.

08:23.783 --> 08:31.070
So the bottom line is is that when we're running hard after God, the blessings will run after us.

08:31.130 --> 08:31.931
You believe that today?

08:32.451 --> 08:36.995
Now today I want to focus on the last key to my series.

08:37.676 --> 08:40.499
