08:41.520 --> 08:42.440
Amen, deception.

08:42.801 --> 08:45.864
How many people know that the devil is the father of lies?

08:46.945 --> 08:52.530
And his whole goal is to deceive people in believing lies.

08:52.802 --> 08:55.104
That's all he can do is try to deceive us.

08:55.965 --> 09:04.894
Sometimes the devil, you know, you're going through a problem and the devil will say to you, of course you think it's your own thoughts, but not every thought that comes to your mind comes from you.

09:04.954 --> 09:08.618
That's a good statement there.

09:09.059 --> 09:14.785
Not every thought that comes to your mind comes by your own.

09:15.065 --> 09:20.050
It might be God speaking to you and the devil can talk to you too.

09:20.514 --> 09:24.018
did not the devil talk to Jesus when he was in the wilderness?

09:24.659 --> 09:27.202
Did he not try to tempt Jesus in the wilderness?

09:27.623 --> 09:35.593
Well the devil will try to talk to us too and you gotta learn and decipher what's you, what's the devil and what's God, amen?

09:36.173 --> 09:38.336
